name: Portrait of Asteraspace
description:
Self-portrait dedicated for Asteraspace 

Asteraspace: I call her Anggi, she is passionate about music and poems (in my opinion) and I'd love her works! So much! I’m very honored to have some of your artworks in my collection!

And, go check her works on https://hicetnunc.art/asteraspace

Pssst.. I’ve never met her in real life :’) Which is, I’m very grateful to be part of this ultra-enchant NFT community!

Hi Anggi, here’s a little gift for you! It’s pleased to meet you here, good luck on your next project & have a great day dear! All hail Taureans! 💜💚 Hihi!

Hand-drawn digitally on procreate
2000x2250 | 400dpi

Personal project
